PET – Strengths and Limitations

Strengths
- good spatial resolution (5-10mm); better than 
ERP/MEG but worse than fMRI

Limitations
- poor temporal resolution
- extremely invasive (injection of radioactive tracer)
- rare & expensive ($3 million, $700K yearly 
maintenance)
- correlational (not causal)

